Minimalist | Black All In One Wedding Invitation

Hot Deals! Minimalist | Black All In One Wedding Invitation – weddings Minimalist quality over price Minimalist quality productsThis minimalist black all in one wedding invitation is perfect for a simple wedding. The modern romantic design features dark black and white typography paired with a rustic yet elegant calligraphy with vintage hand lettered style. Customizable in any color. Keep the design simple and elegant, as is, or personalize it by adding your own graphics and artwork. Save paper by including the details on the back of the wedding invitation instead of on a separate enclosure card. Include the RSVP info as well if your guest will be replying electronically (optional). Price:$1.98
